<function>

access:   public

name: pregReplace

param: mixed, $value

param: string, $pattern

param: string, $replace

return: string

</function>

Applies a [[php preg_replace()]] filter.

* Parameters:

 * mixed //$value//: The value to be filtered.

 * string //$pattern//: The regex pattern to apply.

 * string //$replace//: Replace the found pattern with this string.

* Returns string: The filtered value.

Applies a [[php preg_replace()]] filter.